messages.content: Hello
Salam! Chaman Chutya yahan. Kese madad kar sakta hun apki?
Kya haal hai?
Shukar hai, sab kuch theak hai. Apka kya haal hai?
lat long batao?
Kya aap mujhe zyada tafseelat de sakte hain? Aap kis cheez ka latitude aur longitude chahte hain?
mera lat long ye hai: (24.8661706, 67.0781608)
Kya aapko kisi specific product ko order karna hai ya phir cart checkout karna hai? Agar aap mujhe yeh bata denge, toh mein madad kar sakta hoon!
mera lat long ye hai: (24.8661706, 67.0781608)
Aapka latitude aur longitude sahi hai. Lekin, kya aap kisi specific product ki talash mein hain? Agar haan, toh please mujhe us product ka naam bataein.
mere lat long se meri location nikaal sakte hu?

Mujhe aapki location ka naam nahi pata, lekin aapka latitude aur longitude hai (24.8661706, 67.0781608). Kya aap chahte hain ke mein isse kisi product order karne ya cart checkout karne ke liye istemal karun?
jee daal chaye
Kya aapko thoda aur specific kar sakte hain? Kis qisam ki daal aap dhoond rahe hain, jaise masoor daal, moong daal, ya kisi aur?
masoor
[{"id": 1374, "name": "Lal Masoor Daal 500 gm", "discountedPrice": "152.00", "quantity": 101, "productPurchaseLimit": 5}]

Mujhe "Lal Masoor Daal 500 gm" mil gayi hai. Iski price hai 152.00 rupees aur 101 packets available hain. 

Kya aap is item ko order karna chahenge? Agar haan, toh kitne packets aap chahte hain? (Maximum 5 packets ek order mein purchase kiya ja sakta hai.)
Cart created successfully: {'success': True}
Aapka cart successfully create ho gaya hai. Ab aap checkout karne ke liye ready hain. Kya aap checkout karna chahenge?
jee checkout karlo

Kya aap mujhe delivery details de sakte hain? 
1. City name 
2. Street address 
3. Area/neighborhood name 

Yeh sab details dijiye, taake mein aapka order checkout kar sakun.
latlong se nikal lo
Mujhe aapki exact location ki street address ya area ki information nahi hai. Kya aap mujhe manually yeh details de sakte hain? Ya phir, agar aapko location ka naam pata hai toh woh bata dijiye.
hello
Hello! How can I assist you today?
{"city": "Karachi Division", "street_address": "Tipu Sultan Road", "area": "Jinnah Cooperative Housing Society"}

- **Street Address:** Tipu Sultan Road
